at|^z@3^b@2^^^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|I actually have advocated to be more careful about preempting in 2nd seat. In 3rd seat you should strain to preempt, and even preempt with some minimum opening hands to make it harder for 4th seat to bid. In 1st seat, you should be aggressive, especially when not vulnerable.|
