nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Since I believe you can preempt with an outside 4-card major, South has a clear 2@S opening bid. South has wonderful 6-4 distribution and little defense. It is an ideal preempt. Yes, it turns out that NS have a 9-card heart fit. But first of all that is unlikely. |
