nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|It is much more likely NS would have a spade fit than a heart fit. On average, partner will hold 2-3 spades when you hold a 6-card suit for an 8 or 9-card fit (7/3 = 2.33). On the other hand, on average partner will hold 3 hearts (9/3) when holding a 4-card suit, for a 7-card fit.|
