nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Even on this hand, if South passes, EW can make 4@C. East will open 1@C. North has several choices (1@D, 1@H, or 2NT). My choice is 2NT. That may get NS to 4@H if South is an aggressive bidder. |
